#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:77
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "&kappname; is a logic-based symbol placement puzzle."
msgid "&ksudoku; is a logic-based symbol placement puzzle."
msgstr ""
"&kappname; je logički bazirana slagalica sa simbolima koji imaju određeno "
"mjesto."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:79
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The player has to fill a grid with symbols so that each column, row and "
#| "block on the game board contains only one instance of each symbol. In "
#| "&kappname; the symbols are usually the numbers 1 to 9, but may be the "
#| "letters A to P or A to Y in larger puzzles. Puzzles start with the board "
#| "partially filled and it is your job to fill in the rest."
msgid ""
"The player has to fill a grid with symbols so that each column, row and "
"block on the game board contains only one instance of each symbol. In "
"&ksudoku; the symbols are usually the numbers 1 to 9, but may be the letters "
"A to P or A to Y in larger puzzles. Puzzles start with the board partially "
"filled and it is your job to fill in the rest. Some types of puzzle have "
"less than nine symbols."
msgstr ""
"Igrač mora da popuni rešetku sa simbolima tako da svaka kolona,red i blok na "
"ploči sadrži po jedan element od svakog simbola.\n"
"U &kappname; simboli su obično brojevi od 1-9, ali mogu biti u slova od A-P "
"ili A-Y na velikim slagalicama. Slagalaica je već na samom početku djelimčno "
"popunjena i vaš je posao da popunite ostatak."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:86
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "When you start a game, you can choose from several Sudoku types and "
#| "sizes. You can then have &kappname; generate a puzzle for you to solve or "
#| "you can start with an empty board and enter in a puzzle from another "
#| "source, such as a newspaper, then get &kappname; to check it and maybe "
#| "solve it."
msgid ""
"When you start a game, you can choose from several Sudoku types and sizes. "
"You can then have &ksudoku; generate a puzzle for you to solve or you can "
"start with an empty board and enter in a puzzle from another source, such as "
"a newspaper, then get &ksudoku; to check it and maybe solve it."
msgstr ""
"Kada počnete igrati, možete birati između nekoliko vrsta i veličina Sudoku. "
"Nakon toga će &kappname; generirati zagonetke za vas da  riješiti ili možete "
"započeti s praznom pločom i unijeti u slagalici iz drugog izvora, kao što su "
"novine, onda uzmete &kappname; da provjerite, a možda i  riješi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:92
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "There are many variations of Sudoku in existence and &kappname; provides "
#| "a good selection of them. The most common variant has a 9x9 square grid "
#| "and uses Arabic numerals 1 to 9 as symbols. The grid has 9 rows and 9 "
#| "columns and is divided into 9 blocks of 3x3 squares. The problem is – "
#| "each symbol can only be used once per row, column or block."
msgid ""
"There are many variations of Sudoku in existence and &ksudoku; provides a "
"good selection of them. The most common type, Standard Sudoku, has a 9x9 "
"square grid and uses Arabic numerals 1 to 9 as symbols. The grid has 9 rows "
"and 9 columns and is divided into 9 blocks of 3x3 squares. The problem is – "
"each symbol can only be used once per row, column or block."
msgstr ""
"Postoje mnoge varijacije Sudoku &kappname; pruža dobar izbor od njih."
"Najčešći varijanta ima 9x9 kvadrat mrežu i koristi arapskim brojevima od 1 "
"do 9 kao simbolima .Rešetka ima 9 redaka i stupaca 9 i podijeljen je na 9 "
"blokove 3x3 kvadrata.Problem je - svaki simbol može se koristiti samo jednom "
"po redu,koloni  ili blok."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:99
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It takes time and concentration to complete a game. However, solving Sudoku "
"puzzles helps to increase overall brain activity and therefore is highly "
"recommended."
msgstr ""
"Potrebno je vremena i koncentracije za dovršetak igre. Međutim, rješavanje "
"Sudoku zagonetke pomaže povećati ukupnu aktivnost mozga i stoga se "
"preporučuje."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:105
#, no-c-format
msgid "How to Play"
msgstr "Kako igrati"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:107
#, no-c-format
msgid "Objective:"
msgstr "Cilj:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:107
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Fill the grid so that each column, row and block contains only one instance "
"of each symbol."
msgstr ""
"Ispuniti mrežu tako da svaka kolona ,red i blok sadrži samo jednu instancu "
"svakog simbola."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:111
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "When the game starts you are prompted to choose which game type and board "
#| "size you are interested in. You can enter in a puzzle from another source "
#| "or have &kappname; generate a puzzle. The generator has several "
#| "difficulty settings and some symmetry settings, which affect the pattern "
#| "in which the puzzle is generated. Your game experience will depend on "
#| "which of all these options you choose."
msgid ""
"When the game starts you are prompted to choose which game type and board "
"size you are interested in. You can enter in a puzzle from another source or "
"have &ksudoku; generate a puzzle. The generator has several difficulty "
"settings and some symmetry settings, which affect the pattern in which the "
"puzzle is generated. Your game experience will depend on which of all these "
"options you choose."
msgstr ""
"Kada igra počne se od vas zatraži da odaberete koji tip igre i veličina "
"polja za koje ste  zainteresirani, a možete upisati u slagalici iz nekog "
"drugog izvora, ili će &kappname; generirati zagonetke.Generator ima nekoliko "
"postavki težine i nekih simetrija postavke koje utječu na uzorak u kojem "
"zagonetka je generiran. Vaše iskustvo igra ovisit će o tome koji od svih tih "
"mogućnosti ste izabrali."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:118
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When the puzzle board appears, take a look at the left hand side. There is a "
"selection list which contains all the symbols available in the current game. "
"The set of symbols depends on the size of game you choose. Games may have 4, "
"9, 16 or 25 symbols. The first two sets use the numbers 1 to 4 or 1 to 9: "
"the others use the letters A to P or A to Y."
msgstr ""
"Kada se pojavi ploča sa slagalicom , pogledajte na lijevoj strani. Tu je "
"popis izbora koji sadrži sve simbole dostupne u trenutnoj igri. Skup simbola "
"ovisi o veličini igre koje ste izabrali. Igre mogu imati 4, 9, 16 ili 25 "
"simbola. Prva dva seta koristiti brojevima od 1 do 4 ili 1 do 9: ostali "
"koriste slovima od A do P ili A do Y."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:125
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"First, note the boundaries in the game board. The thick lines outline the "
"blocks. Each of these blocks has to be completed using the symbols available "
"and each symbol must be used once and only once within the block. The same "
"is true of the rows and columns in the board."
msgstr ""
"Prvo, imajte na umu granice u igri odbora. Debeli linije naglašavaju "
"blokova. Svaki od tih blokova mora biti dovršen pomoću dostupni simboli i "
"svaki simbol moraju se koristiti jednom i samo jednom unutar bloka.Isto "
"vrijedi i za kolčone i redove."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:130
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Now you can start entering symbols into the vacant squares on the board. To "
"do that, select the symbol you wish to enter from the selection list on the "
"left, then use the mouse to click on a vacant square in the board. "
"Alternatively, you can hover with the mouse over a vacant square or use the "
"cursor keys to move around, then use the keyboard to enter a symbol."
msgstr ""
"Sada možete početi unosom simbola u polja na ploči. Da biste to postigli, "
"odaberite simbol koji  želite upisati s popisa za  odabira s lijeve strane, "
"a zatim koristite miša kliknite na polje na ploči. Alternativno, možete "
"lebdjeti mišem preko praznog polja ili koristite strelicama za kretanje, a "
"zatim koristite tipkovnicu za unos simbola."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:137
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In Roxdoku (three-dimensional) puzzles, always use the mouse to set a small "
"cube to a value and use a <emphasis>double</emphasis> click. When you rotate "
"the large cube, by clicking and dragging with the mouse, it is easier to see "
"what values are on the small cubes in the background if you click "
"<emphasis>between</emphasis> the small cubes, not on them."
msgstr ""
"U Roxdoku (trodimenzionalni) zagonetki, uvijek koristite miš za postavljanje "
"male kocke  na vrijednost i koristiti <emphasis>dupli </emphasis> klik. Kada "
"rotirati veliku kocku, klikom i povlačenjem miša, lakše je vidjeti što su "
"vrijednosti na kockice u pozadini, ako kliknete <emphasis>između </emphasis> "
"male kockice, a ne na njih."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:144
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "It is useful sometimes to enter markers or notes, which are tiny symbols "
#| "within a square. These have no influence on the solution, but they can "
#| "help you keep track of ideas you have had, especially when there is a "
#| "choice between two alternatives and you do not yet have enough "
#| "information to decide between them. To enter a marker or note, click with "
#| "the right mouse button or hold down the &Shift; key when using the "
#| "keyboard."
msgid ""
"It is useful sometimes to enter markers or notes, which are tiny symbols "
"within a square. These have no influence on the solution, but they can help "
"you keep track of ideas you have had, especially when there is a choice "
"between two alternatives and you do not yet have enough information to "
"decide between them. To enter a marker or note, click with the &RMB; or hold "
"down the &Shift; key when using the keyboard."
msgstr ""
"Korisno je  ponekad ući markere ili bilješke, koji su sitni simboli unutar "
"kvadrata. Oni nemaju utjecaja na rješenje, ali mogu vam pomoći pratiti ideje "
"koje ste imali, pogotovo kada je izbor između dvije alternative, a vi još "
"uvijek nemaju dovoljno informacija kako bi odlučiti između njih. Za unos "
"marker ili bilješku, kliknite desnom tipkom miša ili držite &Shift; tipku "
"kada koristite tipkovnicu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:152
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "To clear symbols from a square, hover over the square with the mouse and "
#| "hit <keycap>Delete</keycap> or <keycap>Backspace</keycap> on the keyboard "
#| "or click with the &RMB; on the square."
msgid ""
"To clear symbols from a square, hover over the square with the mouse and hit "
"&Del; or &Backspace; on the keyboard or click with the &RMB; on the square."
msgstr ""
"Za brisanje simbola s polja , lebdjeti iznad polja s mišem i pritisnuti "
"<keycap> Izbriši </keycap> ili <keycap> Nazad</keycap> na tastaturi ili "
"kliknite sa &RMB; Na polje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:156
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Notice that the squares change color while you hover the mouse over them. "
#| "This is to help you keep up with the rules of &kappname;. Use the "
#| "vertical and horizontal lines to check if the symbol you are about to "
#| "enter into a vacant spot is already in use anywhere in the vertical or "
#| "horizontal line that square is a part of. The coloring also highlights "
#| "the block which, if you remember, must also contain only one instance of "
#| "each symbol. If you do not need the highlighting, you can use the "
#| "<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Configure "
#| "&kappname;...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item to turn it off."
msgid ""
"Notice that the squares change color while you hover the mouse over them. "
"This is to help you keep up with the rules of &ksudoku;. Use the vertical "
"and horizontal lines to check if the symbol you are about to enter into a "
"vacant spot is already in use anywhere in the vertical or horizontal line "
"that square is a part of. The coloring also highlights the block which, if "
"you remember, must also contain only one instance of each symbol. If you do "
"not need the highlighting, you can use the <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Configure &ksudoku;…</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu "
"item to turn it off."
msgstr ""
"Uočite da su kvadrati promijeniti boju dok prelazite mišem preko njih. To je "
"da vam pomognemo s pravilima &kappname;. Koristite vertikalne i horizontalne "
"linije za provjeru je li je simbol koji želite unijeti već korišten u "
"vertikanoj ili horizontalnoj liniji na ploči ili njeom dijelu .Bojanje "
"također naglašava blok koji, ako se sjećate, mora sadržavati samo jednu "
"instancu svakog simbola. Ako vam ne treba isticanje, možete koristiti "
"<menuchoice> <guimenu> Postavke </guimenu> <guimenuitem> Konfiguracija "
"&kappname; ... </guimenuitem> </menuchoice> Stavku menia da biste ga "
"isključili."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:167
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Keep entering symbols in accordance with the rules until the whole game "
#| "field is filled up. At this point &kappname; will check if all the "
#| "entries are valid and will either correct you or accept your solution."
msgid ""
"Keep entering symbols in accordance with the rules until the whole game "
"field is filled up. At this point &ksudoku; will check if all the entries "
"are valid and will either correct you or accept your solution."
msgstr ""
"Držite unos simbola u skladu s pravilima dok cijela ploča ne bude "
"popunjena . U ovom trenutku &kappname; će provjeriti jesu li sve stavke "
"uredu  i da li  će vas  ispraviti ili prihvatiti rješenje."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:173
#, no-c-format
msgid "Game Rules, Strategies and Tips"
msgstr "Pravila igre, Strategije i savjeti"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:175
#, no-c-format
msgid "General Game Rules"
msgstr "Generalna Pravila Igre"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:177
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "The rules of &kappname; are quite simple."
msgid "The rules of &ksudoku; are quite simple."
msgstr "Pravila &kappname; su vemo jednostavna."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:179
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Depending on the size of the game board, the type of puzzle and the "
#| "difficulty level chosen an individual &kappname; puzzle may take from a "
#| "few minutes to a few hours to solve."
msgid ""
"Depending on the size of the game board, the type of puzzle and the "
"difficulty level chosen an individual &ksudoku; puzzle may take from a few "
"minutes to a few hours to solve."
msgstr ""
"Ovisno o veličini ploče na kojoj se igra, vrsta slagalice i stupanj težine "
"koja je izabrana pojedine &kappname; slagalice može trajati od nekoliko "
"minuta do nekoliko sati da se riješi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:183
#, no-c-format
msgid "Each square may hold one and only one symbol."
msgstr "Svaki kvadrat može održati jedan i samo jedan simbol."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:185
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Each horizontal row (as defined by the game board) can contain each symbol "
"exactly once."
msgstr ""
"Svaki vodoravni red (kao što je definirano sa igrom na ploči) mogu "
"sadržavati svaki simbol točno jednom."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:187
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Each vertical column (as defined by the game board) can contain each symbol "
"exactly once."
msgstr ""
"Svaki vertikalna kolona (kao što je definirano sa igrom na ploči) može "
"sadržavati svaki simbol točno jednom."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:189
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Each block (as defined by the game board) can contain each symbol exactly "
"once"
msgstr ""
"Svaki blok (kao što je definirano s igrom na ploči) mogu sadržavati svaki "
"simbol točno jednom."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:193 index.docbook:627
#, no-c-format
msgid "Note:"
msgstr "Napomena:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:193
#, no-c-format
msgid "The set of symbols depends on the size of game you choose."
msgstr "Set simbola ovis o veličini ploče na kojoj se igra."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:198
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Knowledge of mathematics or language is not required to solve &kappname; "
#| "puzzles."
msgid ""
"Knowledge of mathematics or language is not required to solve &ksudoku; "
"puzzles, but a little ability with arithmetic is needed in Killer Sudoku and "
"Mathdoku puzzles."
msgstr ""
"Poznavanje mmatematike ili jezika je nepotrebno za riješavanje &kappname; "
"slagalica."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:202
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The symbols already on the game board when the puzzle starts cannot be "
"changed."
msgstr "Simboli koji su već na ploči kad aigra starta se ne mogu promijeniti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:204
#, no-c-format
msgid "You can only modify the symbols you have previously entered."
msgstr "Mogu se smao promijenit simboli koji su nedavni dodani."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:206
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Puzzles generated by &kappname; have one solution only."
msgid "Puzzles generated by &ksudoku; have one solution only."
msgstr "Slagalice generisne &kappname; imaju smao jedni riješenje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:208
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Puzzles you enter in might have no solution or more than one solution, but "
"if they are from a published source this probably means you have made a data-"
"entry error."
msgstr ""
"Slagalice koje vi unesete možda nemaju riješenje ili ih imaju više, ali "
"akosu oni  iz objavljene literature to vjerojatno znači da ste napravili "
"pogrešku unos podataka."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:215
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "&kappname; Variations"
msgid "&ksudoku; Variations"
msgstr "&kappname; Variations"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:217
#, no-c-format
msgid "Sudoku Puzzles"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:220
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Standard 9x9 Sudoku puzzle has 9 rows, 9 columns and 9 square blocks of "
"size 3x3."
msgstr ""
"Standard 9x9 Sudoku slagalica ima 9 redova, 9 kolona i 9 kvadrata od "
"veličine 3x3."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:222
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Other sizes of Standard Sudoku are 4x4 (very easy), 16x16 and 25x25 (not so "
"easy)."
msgstr ""
"Druge veličine Sudokua su 4x4(veoma lagano),16x16 i 25x25(ne tako lagano)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:224
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The Jigsaw variation is the same as Standard Sudoku except that some "
#| "blocks are not square."
msgid ""
"The Jigsaw and Aztec variations are the same as Standard 9x9 Sudoku except "
"that some blocks are not square."
msgstr ""
"Jigsaw verzija je  Standardni  Sudoku osim što neki blokovi nisu kvadrati."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:226
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The XSudoku variation is exactly the same as Standard Sudoku with an "
#| "additional requirement: the two main diagonals must also each contain the "
#| "symbols 1 to 9 once and once only. &kappname; highlights the diagonals to "
#| "make this easier to see."
msgid ""
"The XSudoku variation is exactly the same as Standard Sudoku with an "
"additional requirement: the two main diagonals must also each contain the "
"symbols 1 to 9 once and once only. &ksudoku; highlights the diagonals to "
"make this easier to see."
msgstr ""
"XSudoku varijanta je potpuno identican  Standardom Sudoku sa dodatnim "
"zahtjevom:dvije glavne dijagonale moraju isto sadržavati simbole 1-9 jednom "
"i samo jednom. &kappname; osvijetli dijagonalu da stvar ucini lakšom."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:231
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The Jigsaw variation is the same as Standard Sudoku except that some "
#| "blocks are not square."
msgid ""
"The Nonomino 9x9, Pentomino 5x5 and Tetromino 4x4 variations are the same as "
"a Standard Sudoku except that some blocks are not square."
msgstr ""
"Jigsaw verzija je  Standardni  Sudoku osim što neki blokovi nisu kvadrati."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:234
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The Jigsaw variation is the same as Standard Sudoku except that some "
#| "blocks are not square."
msgid ""
"The 6x6 variation is the same as a Standard Sudoku except that the blocks "
"are six 3x2 rectangles."
msgstr ""
"Jigsaw verzija je  Standardni  Sudoku osim što neki blokovi nisu kvadrati."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:240
#, no-c-format
msgid "Samurai Puzzles"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:243
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The Samurai Sudoku consists of five Standard Sudoku puzzles of 9x9 "
#| "squares each, overlapping at the corners by four 3x3 blocks. Each of the "
#| "five puzzles has 9 rows and 9 columns to solve, but there are only 41 "
#| "blocks to solve, rather than 45, because of the overlap."
msgid ""
"The Samurai Sudoku consists of five Standard Sudoku puzzles of 9x9 squares "
"each, overlapping at the corners by four 3x3 blocks. Each of the five "
"puzzles has 9 rows, 9 columns and 9 blocks to solve and the symbols in the "
"overlapping squares must fit into the solutions of two Standard 9x9 Sudokus."
msgstr ""
"Samurai Sudoku sastoji od pet standard Sudoku zagonetke 9x9 kvadrata svaki, "
"preklapaju na uglovima po četiri 3x3 blokova. Svaki od pet zagonetke ima 9 "
"redova i  9 kolona za riješiti, ali ima samo 41 blokova za riješiti, a ne "
"45, zbog preklapanja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:249
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The Tiny Samurai Sudoku consists of five 4x4 puzzles, overlapping at the "
#| "corners by four squares. Each of the five puzzles has 4 rows, 4 columns "
#| "and 4 blocks to solve."
msgid ""
"The Tiny Samurai Sudoku contains five 4x4 Sudoku puzzles, overlapping at the "
"corners by four squares. Each of the five puzzles has 4 rows, 4 columns and "
"4 blocks to solve."
msgstr ""
"Tiny Samurai Sudoku sastoji od pet 4x4 zagonetke, preklapaju na uglovima "
"četiri kvadrata. Svaki od pet zagonetke ima 4 reda, 4 kolone i 4 bloka za "
"riješiti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:253
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Windmill variation consists of five Standard 9x9 Sudoku puzzles, "
"overlapping at the corners by two 3x3 blocks. It is like a Samurai Sudoku, "
"but the central 9x9 Sudoku is harder to see. Eight of its 3x3 blocks are "
"shared with the sails of the windmill and only the central 3x3 block is not."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:259
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Sohei variation is another Samurai type and has four 9x9 Sudoku puzzles, "
"overlapping at two corners by a 3x3 block. The central 3x3 block of the "
"puzzle is empty."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:266
#, no-c-format
msgid "Roxdoku 3D Puzzles"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:269
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The Roxdoku variations are based on cubes in three dimensions, but are "
#| "easier than they sound. There are no rows or columns. A 3x3x3 Roxdoku "
#| "puzzle has 27 small cubes arranged into a larger 3x3x3 cube. This "
#| "contains nine slices, each containing 3x3 small cubes, and these are the "
#| "square blocks that must be filled with the numbers 1 to 9. A 4x4x4 "
#| "Roxdoku has twelve 4x4 slices and a 5x5x5 Roxdoku has fifteen 5x5 slices."
msgid ""
"The Roxdoku variants are based on cubes in three dimensions, but are easier "
"than they sound. There are no rows or columns. A 3x3x3 Roxdoku puzzle has 27 "
"small cubes arranged into a larger 3x3x3 cube. This contains nine slices, "
"each containing 3x3 small cubes, and these are the square blocks that must "
"be filled with the numbers 1 to 9. A 4x4x4 Roxdoku has twelve 4x4 slices and "
"a 5x5x5 Roxdoku has fifteen 5x5 slices."
msgstr ""
"Varijacije Roxdoku se temelji na kocki u tri dimenzije, ali su lakše nego "
"što zvuči. Nema redova ili koloba .3x3x3 Roxdoku zagonetka ima 27 kockice "
"posložene u većim 3x3x3 kockama. Sadrži devet kriške, svaki sadrži 3x3 "
"kockice, a to su četvornih blokova koje moraju biti ispunjene brojevima od 1 "
"do 9. 4x4x4 Roxdoku ima dvanaest 4x4 kriške i 5x5x5 Roxdoku ima petnaest 5x5 "
"kriške."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:277
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Roxdoku Twin variant has two 3x3x3 Roxdoku puzzles sharing a corner. The "
"corner piece must be part of the solution of both 3x3x3 cubes."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:280
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Double Roxdoku variant contains two 3x3x3 Roxdoku puzzles sharing three "
"pieces along an edge. The edge pieces must be part of the solution of both "
"3x3x3 cubes."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:284
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Samurai Roxdoku variant has nine 3x3x3 Roxdoku puzzles. One is at the "
"center and the other eight 3x3x3 cubes overlap it, one at each of the "
"central cube's corners. Those corner pieces must each be part of the "
"solution of two 3x3x3 cubes."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:292
#, no-c-format
msgid "Killer and Mathdoku Variations"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:295
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Killer puzzles have two variants: Tiny Killer (4x4) and Killer Sudoku (9x9). "
"They both have rows, columns and square blocks, exactly as in Standard "
"Sudoku puzzles and following exactly the same rules. They also have "
"irregularly shaped areas called cages, where each cage's digits must add up "
"to the number in small type in the corner of the cage and no digit can be "
"repeated within the cage. Typically the puzzle starts with only a few "
"squares containing symbols. You need to use arithmetic and the usual Sudoku "
"rules together to work out the solution. The screen graphics make it "
"difficult to visualize the square blocks that are present, but they are "
"easier to see if you print the puzzle, using the <menuchoice><guimenu>Game</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Print…</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:311
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Mathdoku variants, also known as <trademark>Kenken</trademark>, have no "
"blocks, only row and column restrictions, and have cages where the digits "
"must add, subtract, divide or multiply according to the values and "
"arithmetical symbols in small type in their corners. A digit in a Mathdoku "
"cage can be repeated, but not in the same column or row. For example, an L-"
"shape of three squares with a requirement 5+ can have solutions 1 3 1 or 2 1 "
"2, provided the ones or twos are not in the same row or column as each "
"other. Note that subtraction and division cages always have two squares and "
"the two digits of the solution can appear in either order. For example, a 2-"
"cage could have solutions 1 3 or 3 1 or 2 4 or 4 2, &etc;"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:325
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Because there are no blocks in a Mathdoku puzzle, it can have any size from "
"3x3 up to 9x9, with the default being 6x6. See the <link linkend="
"\"configuration\">Game Configuration</link> section for details. To get you "
"started, there is a variant called Mathdoku 101 of size 4x4."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:335
#, no-c-format
msgid "Strategies and Tips"
msgstr "Strategije i savjeti"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:338
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Take your time and do not rush. &kappname; is not a quick game."
msgid "Take your time and do not rush. &ksudoku; is not a quick game."
msgstr "Izdvojite vremena i nemojte žuriti. &kappname; nije brza igra."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:340
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Pay attention to the row, column, and block colorings. They are there to "
"help you."
msgstr ""
"Obratiti pozornost na boje redova ,kolona i blokova. Oni su tu da vam "
"pomognu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:342
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Make sure that no duplicate symbol exists already in the row, column or "
"block where you are entering a symbol."
msgstr ""
"Uvjerite se da nema duplih  simbola koji već postoji u redu, koloni ili blok "
"gdje se upisuje simbol."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:345
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If in doubt, try to foresee if a square you are entering a symbol into may "
"be needed by some other symbol, which otherwise cannot go anywhere else due "
"to the row, column and block rules."
msgstr ""
"Ako ste u nedoumici, pokušajte predvidjetda li  simbol koji unosite  može "
"biti potreban u nekom drugom polju, koji se inače ne mogu ići bilo gdje "
"drugdje, zbog pravila redova, kolona i blokova."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:349
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the Internet to search for general hints and strategies for solving "
"Sudoku puzzles."
msgstr ""
"Koristite internet za traženje generalnih upota i strategija kako riješiti "
"Sudoku slagalice."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:351
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use marker moves when you spot a square or squares that have just a few "
"alternatives but you cannot decide between them immediately. Markers will "
"save you time and memory effort later, when more squares have been filled "
"in. See <link linkend=\"howto\"> How to Play</link> for details of how to "
"use markers."
msgstr ""
"Koristite marker poteza kada uočite da polje moze imati nekoliko mogućnosti, "
"ali ne može odlučiti između njih odmah. Markeri će vam uštedjeti vrijeme i "
"trud memorije kasnije, kad više kvadrata su popunjena. Pogledajte <link "
"linkend=\"howto\"> Kako igrati</link> za detalje o tome kako koristiti "
"markera."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:358
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If you are having trouble, try to retrace your steps and see exactly "
#| "where you have made an error. You can use the <menuchoice><guimenu>Move</"
#| "guimenu> <guimenuitem>Undo</guimenuitem></menuchoice> and "
#| "<menuchoice><guimenu>Move</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Redo</guimenuitem></"
#| "menuchoice> menu items, repeatedly if necessary, and there is a setting "
#| "in <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Configure "
#| "&kappname;...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> that highlights errors."
msgid ""
"If you are having trouble, try to retrace your steps and see exactly where "
"you have made an error. You can use the <menuchoice><guimenu>Move</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Undo</guimenuitem></menuchoice> and <menuchoice><guimenu>Move</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Redo</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu items, repeatedly "
"if necessary, and there is a setting in <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Configure &ksudoku;…</guimenuitem></menuchoice> that "
"highlights errors."
msgstr ""
"Ako imate problema, pokušajte vratiti korake nazad da vidite gdje ste "
"napravili grešku. Možete koristiti <menuchoice><guimenu>Potez</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Nazad</guimenuitem></menuchoice> i <menuchoice><guimenu>Potez</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Ponovi</guimenuitem></menuchoice> meni stavke, ako je "
"potrebno , i ima stavka u postvkama <menuchoice><guimenu>Postavke </guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Konfiguriši &kappname;...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> svjetlinu "
"grešaka."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:368
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Even though &kappname; provides a 'Hint' option for you, try not to use "
#| "it often. Remember, solving the puzzle all by yourself enhances your "
#| "brain activity, while using the 'Hint' feature too often is cheating."
msgid ""
"Even though &ksudoku; provides a 'Hint' option for you, try not to use it "
"often. Remember, solving the puzzle all by yourself enhances your brain "
"activity, while using the 'Hint' feature too often is cheating."
msgstr ""
"Čak i ako &kappname; omogućuje 'Hint' opciju za vas,ne koristite je često. "
"Zapamtite, riješavajući slagalicu samostalno potpomazete razvijanju vašeg "
"mozga, korištenje dodatka 'Hint' prečesto ej varanje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:373
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have too much trouble solving a certain puzzle and simply must use "
"the 'Hint' feature, then maybe you should try decreasing the difficulty "
"level, or try a simpler, more basic puzzle."
msgstr ""
"Ako imte prviše problema riješavakući trenutnu slagilcu jednistavno "
"pritisnite 'Hint' dodatak onda mi mozda mogli pokušati smanjiti razinu igre, "
"ili probati lakšum,jednostavniju slagalicu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:377
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Some puzzle layouts feature very specific game board shapes. It is a good "
"idea to have the highlighting option enabled even if you consider yourself "
"an experienced player."
msgstr ""
"Neke slagalice imaju vrlo specifičan izglen na ploči. To je dobra je ideja "
"da imete istaknute opcije  čak i ako ste i sami iskusan igrač."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:385
#, no-c-format
msgid "Interface Overview"
msgstr "Pregled izgleda"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:387
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Welcome Screen"
msgstr "Welcome Ekran"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:389
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The Welcome Screen is the first thing you see when you start &kappname; "
#| "or use the toolbar or menu to request a new game. It has a list of all "
#| "the puzzle types and sizes and you can click on one of them to make a "
#| "selection."
msgid ""
"The Welcome Screen is the first thing you see when you start &ksudoku; or "
"use the toolbar or menu to request a new game. It has a list of all the "
"puzzle types and sizes and you can click on one of them to make a selection."
msgstr ""
"Welcome ekran je prva stvar koju vidite kada pokrente &kappname;ili "
"koristite alatnu traku ili meni zbog zahtjeva za novu igru. Ima lista svih "
"tipova slagalica i veličina i možete kliknuti na neki od njih kako bi "
"obavili vaš izbor."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:394
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If you click the button marked <guilabel>Enter In A Puzzle</guilabel>, an "
#| "empty board of the selected type and size appears. Here you can use the "
#| "mouse or keyboard to enter in a puzzle from another source, such as a "
#| "newspaper. When you have finished, use the <guilabel>Check</guilabel> "
#| "action, on toolbar or menu, to check the puzzle. It should have just one "
#| "solution. If so, you can start solving the puzzle or perhaps get "
#| "&kappname; to solve it. If there is no solution or more than one "
#| "solution, it probably means you have made a data-entry error somewhere."
msgid ""
"If you click the button marked <guibutton>Enter In A Puzzle</guibutton>, an "
"empty board of the selected type and size appears. Here you can use the "
"mouse or keyboard to enter in a puzzle from another source, such as a "
"newspaper. When you have finished, use the <guilabel>Check</guilabel> "
"action, on toolbar or menu, to check the puzzle. It should have just one "
"solution. If so, you can start solving the puzzle or perhaps get &ksudoku; "
"to solve it. If there is no solution or more than one solution, it probably "
"means you have made a data-entry error somewhere."
msgstr ""
"Ako kliknete na gumb s oznakom <guilabel> Ulaz u puzzle </guilabel>, pojavi "
"prazna odbor odabranoj vrsti i veličini. Ovdje možete koristiti miš ili "
"tipkovnicu za unos u slagalici iz drugog izvora, kao što su novine. Kad ste "
"završili, koristite <guilabel> Provjerite </guilabel> akciju, na alatnoj "
"traci ili izbornik, provjeriti zagonetku. To bi trebao imati samo jedno "
"rješenje. Ako je tako, možete početi rješavati zagonetke ili možda će "
"&kappname; to riješiti. Ako ne postoji rješenje ili više od jednog rješenja, "
"to vjerojatno znači da ste napravili pogrešku unos podataka negdje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:404
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If you click the button marked <guilabel>Generate A Puzzle</guilabel>, "
#| "&kappname; will display a board with some squares already filled in. It "
#| "is up to you to fill in the rest."
msgid ""
"If you click the button marked <guibutton>Generate A Puzzle</guibutton>, "
"&ksudoku; will display a board with some squares already filled in. It is up "
"to you to fill in the rest."
msgstr ""
"Ako pritisnete dugme  <guilabel>Generiši slagalicu </guilabel>, &kappname; "
"će prikazati ploču sa nekim poljima koja su već popunjena. Na vama je na "
"popunite ostatak."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:408
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Before you generate a puzzle, check that the settings of the "
#| "<guilabel>Difficulty</guilabel> and <guilabel>Symmetry</guilabel> buttons "
#| "are to your liking. You can change them during a game, but then they will "
#| "have no effect until the next puzzle is generated."
msgid ""
"Before you generate a puzzle, check that the settings of the "
"<guilabel>Difficulty:</guilabel> and <guilabel>Symmetry:</guilabel> drop "
"down boxes are to your liking. You can change them during a game, but then "
"they will have no effect until the next puzzle is generated."
msgstr ""
"Prije nego što generirati zagonetke, provjerite jesu li postavke <guilabel> "
"Težina </guilabel> i <guilabel> Simetrija </guilabel> tipke kako bi vi "
"željeli . Možete ih mijenjati tijekom igre, ali onda oni neće imati učinka "
"dok se  sljedeća zagonetka generira."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:414
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If you cannot see the <guilabel>Difficulty</guilabel> and "
#| "<guilabel>Symmetry</guilabel> buttons, use the "
#| "<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Show Statusbar</"
#| "guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item to make sure that the statusbar is "
#| "visible."
msgid ""
"If you cannot see the <guilabel>Difficulty:</guilabel> and "
"<guilabel>Symmetry:</guilabel> drop down boxes, use the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Show Statusbar</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item to make sure that the statusbar is "
"visible."
msgstr ""
"Ako ne možete vidjeti <guilabel> Težina </guilabel> i <guilabel> Simetrija </"
"guilabel> tipke, koristite <menuchoice> <guimenu> Postavke </guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem> Prikaži statusbar </guimenuitem> </menuchoice> stavku "
"izbornika kako bi bili sigurni da statusbar vidljiv."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:420
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The <guilabel>Difficulty</guilabel> button provides six levels of "
#| "difficulty, from <guimenuitem>Very Easy</guimenuitem> up to "
#| "<guimenuitem>Hard</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Diabolical</guimenuitem> "
#| "and <guimenuitem>Unlimited</guimenuitem>. The easier levels may take a "
#| "few minutes to solve on a 9x9 board. The <guimenuitem>Hard</guimenuitem> "
#| "and <guimenuitem>Diabolical</guimenuitem> levels may take an hour or so "
#| "and are intended to be equivalent to difficult grades appearing in "
#| "newspapers. Samurai puzzles and 16x16 or 25x25 sizes of puzzles will take "
#| "longer to solve, simply because there are more rows, columns and blocks "
#| "and more squares to fill in."
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Difficulty:</guilabel> drop down box provides six levels of "
"difficulty, from <guimenuitem>Very Easy</guimenuitem> up to "
"<guimenuitem>Hard</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Diabolical</guimenuitem> and "
"<guimenuitem>Unlimited</guimenuitem>. The easier levels may take a few "
"minutes to solve on a 9x9 board. The <guimenuitem>Hard</guimenuitem> and "
"<guimenuitem>Diabolical</guimenuitem> levels may take an hour or so and are "
"intended to be equivalent to difficult grades appearing in newspapers. "
"Samurai puzzles and 16x16 or 25x25 sizes of puzzles will take longer to "
"solve, simply because there are more rows, columns and blocks and more "
"squares to fill in."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel> Teškoća </guilabel> tipka daje šest razina težine, od "
"<guimenuitem> Vrlo lako </guimenuitem> do <guimenuitem> Hard </guimenuitem>, "
"<guimenuitem> đavolski </guimenuitem> i <guimenuitem> Neograničeno </"
"guimenuitem>. Lakše razina može potrajati nekoliko minuta da se riješi na "
"9x9 ploči.<guimenuitem> Teško </guimenuitem> i <guimenuitem> đavolski </"
"guimenuitem> razina može potrajati sat vremena, a namijenjeni su da se "
"ekvivalentna teškim nivoima koji se pojavljuju u novinama. Samurai zagonetke "
"i 16x16 ili 25x25 veličine zagonetke će trebati više vremena za rješavanje, "
"jednostavno zato što postoji više redaka, stupaca i blokova i više kvadrata "
"za ispuniti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:430
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The Diabolical level typically requires one or more guesses, with "
#| "backtracking if you guess wrong. Lower levels can usually be solved by "
#| "logic alone. The Unlimited level has no limits on the number of guesses "
#| "required, how soon the first guess is needed or how complex the logic "
#| "might be. It is provided for the interest of expert players, but tends to "
#| "generate uninteresting 'inhuman' puzzles and is not recommended for "
#| "general use."
msgid ""
"The <guimenuitem>Diabolical</guimenuitem> level typically requires one or "
"more guesses, with backtracking if you guess wrong. Lower levels can usually "
"be solved by logic alone. The <guimenuitem>Unlimited</guimenuitem> level has "
"no limits on the number of guesses required, how soon the first guess is "
"needed or how complex the logic might be. It is provided for the interest of "
"expert players, but tends to generate uninteresting <quote>inhuman</quote> "
"puzzles and is not recommended for general use."
msgstr ""
"Dijabolički nivo obično zahtijeva jedno ili više pogađanja, uz vraćanje "
"nazad ako krivo pogodite. Niži nivoi se obično mogu riješiti po samoj "
"logici. Neograničeni nivou nemaju  ograničenja na broj pogodaka koji je  "
"potreban, kako je prije prve pretpostavke   potrebno ili koliko je složeno "
"logika može biti. To omogućeno za interes  stručnih igrača, ali ima "
"tendenciju da se generira nezanimljive 'neljudske' zagonetke i ne preporuča "
"za opću uporabu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:439
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The <guilabel>Symmetry</guilabel> button provides seven types of "
#| "symmetry, including <guimenuitem>No Symmetry</guimenuitem>. This controls "
#| "the layout and appearance of the squares that are filled in at the start "
#| "of a puzzle and has mainly aesthetic effect, except that puzzles with no "
#| "symmetry tend to be slightly harder than those with high symmetry and it "
#| "is less likely that &kappname; can generate a puzzle with high difficulty "
#| "and high symmetry combined."
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Symmetry:</guilabel> drop down box provides seven types of "
"symmetry, including <guimenuitem>No Symmetry</guimenuitem>. This controls "
"the layout and appearance of the squares that are filled in at the start of "
"a puzzle and has mainly aesthetic effect, except that puzzles with no "
"symmetry tend to be slightly harder than those with high symmetry and it is "
"less likely that &ksudoku; can generate a puzzle with high difficulty and "
"high symmetry combined."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel> Simetrija </guilabel> tipka nudi sedam vrsta simetrije, "
"uključujući <guimenuitem> Ne Simetrija </guimenuitem>. To kontrolira izgled "
"i izgled trgova koji su ispunili na početku zagonetka i ima uglavnom "
"estetski učinak, osim što zbunjuje bez simetrije imaju tendenciju da se malo "
"teže nego one s visokim simetrije i to je manje vjerojatno da &kappname; "
"može generirati zagonetke s visokim poteškoća i visoke simetrije u "
"kombinaciji."

